{"id": "ChIJi01KZiPbwoARAn26AjUw2E8", "rating": 4.5, "userRatingCount": 43, "displayName": {"text": "Charlie's Tea 茶理宜世（San Gabriel）", "languageCode": "zh"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJi01KZiPbwoARAn26AjUw2E8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkSmNrWk5jbEp2U2pKR05WVlpPVEZUWTB4WWJYYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Really enjoyed the drinks here! Super refreshing, not too sweet, and the tea flavor was great. Cute presentation and friendly service too. Will definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Really enjoyed the drinks here! Super refreshing, not too sweet, and the tea flavor was great. Cute presentation and friendly service too. Will definitely come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jennie Xu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107665448250760372460/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcSmsx4EF3RPwlNi0IDu8SsdT9nP8Hx8K4VMh9WdW9SsHOtA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-09T21:38:42.188088689Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkSmNrWk5jbEp2U2pKR05WVlpPVEZUWTB4WWJYYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pkSmNrWk5jbEp2U2pKR05WVlpPVEZUWTB4WWJYYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db23664a4d8b:0x4fd8303502ba7d02"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi01KZiPbwoARAn26AjUw2E8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paZmVFWjJia0p4U2tkRVVrTkpabGRXYUZGcmIxRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Grand opening in April 2026. I heard Charlie’s Tea is a popular drink spot in China.\n\nI ordered the Ceylon Black with pecan cream top and the Misty Peach Oolong Milk Tea, which are among their top five drinks. I liked the Peach Oolong much more—it was smooth, with a rich tea flavor and a nice hint of peach. It actually reminded me of Molly Tea.\n\nThe Ceylon Black tasted more like a regular milk tea with cream, not as flavorful as the Peach Oolong.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Grand opening in April 2026. I heard Charlie’s Tea is a popular drink spot in China.\n\nI ordered the Ceylon Black with pecan cream top and the Misty Peach Oolong Milk Tea, which are among their top five drinks. I liked the Peach Oolong much more—it was smooth, with a rich tea flavor and a nice hint of peach. It actually reminded me of Molly Tea.\n\nThe Ceylon Black tasted more like a regular milk tea with cream, not as flavorful as the Peach Oolong.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Ada W", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111728507229811391951/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUl7Am9552xLKXwCGLpUn4OJ9LMdAZMDTZMV2xgN-st52AGnsE=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-02T00:40:59.039696766Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paZmVFWjJia0p4U2tkRVVrTkpabGRXYUZGcmIxRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2paZmVFWjJia0p4U2tkRVVrTkpabGRXYUZGcmIxRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2db23664a4d8b:0x4fd8303502ba7d02"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi01KZiPbwoARAn26AjUw2E8/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xOYVVYY3RWakpIZEZkQk5VdG1jSFIzV1ZoT2FVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "refreshing drinks and super friendly staff! love coming here!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "refreshing drinks and super friendly staff! love coming here!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Yvonne Chu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108869940670224324443/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrenWTSLbF8U2yS20N8kFGOnwAclijyz6kqyc8fWGatmswJ4On=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-19T04:4